spec_data.Name: perl-Class-C3-Componentised
spec_data.Description:
This will inject base classes to your module using the Class::C3 method
resolution order.

Please note: these are not plugins that can take precedence over methods
declared in MyModule. If you want something like that, consider
MooseX::Object::Pluggable.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 08:37:27 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Load mix-ins or components to your C3-based class
